Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.96,0:01:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The flow of time is woven into the warp.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.34,0:01:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,As the seasons turn, it is dyed sky-blue.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.59,0:01:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The callings of man are woven into the weft.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.59,0:01:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Every step upon the earth, each trembling of the heart.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.31,0:01:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Iorph weave together each passing day.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:22.10,0:01:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the centuries of our long, distant lifetimes.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:43.00,0:01:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.50,0:01:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you even doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.97,0:01:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never finish if you keep goofing off.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.10,0:02:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on, Maquia! Jump on in!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.81,0:02:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.44,0:02:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Scaredy-cat!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.57,0:02:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia, you don't need to \Nplay along with that shrew.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.95,0:02:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Krim...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.66,0:02:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia really is...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.25,0:02:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who live their lives weaving cloth, \Nseparate from civilization, were called thus—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The Clan of Partings.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever is the matter, Elder Racine?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:49.90,0:02:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.57,0:02:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it or not, you're jumping next time, Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.99,0:02:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed you!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.25,0:03:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You mustn't handle the cloth so roughly.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.84,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, you're soaked.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, did you manage to pick any good flowers?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.13,0:03:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we should be able to extract a nice, deep color.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia, goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.56,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The thread...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.67,0:03:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.84,0:03:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.18,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Despite my presence?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.51,0:04:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder, I didn't mean—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.68,0:04:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so quick to tears.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.44,0:04:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know why we are called the Clan of Partings?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.40,0:04:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Due to our seemingly unchanging \Nappearances and our long lifespans,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.74,0:04:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,those who do not share our traits \Nview us as beings of legend.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.33,0:04:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Until a few short centuries ago, \Ncreatures like us could be found everywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.04,0:04:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,People who grew wings like birds.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.34,0:04:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Flowers that sang before dawn.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.30,0:04:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Giant fish that delivered goods through waterways.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.22,0:04:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.80,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them have since parted from this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.06,0:04:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, we have a duty to continue weaving the Hibiol.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.65,0:04:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as you live here, you are not alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.32,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hibiol will always remember the moments that silently fade from memory with time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.95,0:05:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who have met with their final farewells will forever be there within the Hibiol, ready to cry with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll really cry with me?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.92,0:05:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you someday depart from Iorph...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.39,0:05:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are ever to connect \Nwith one from the world outside,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.64,0:05:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you mustn't fall in love.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.31,0:05:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love, you will become truly alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.40,0:05:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be alone even though \NI connected with someone?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.53,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,For that is the fate that we of the \NClan of Partings have been bestowed.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.96,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night, Maquia.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.21,0:05:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not forget to weave today's Hibiol.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:58.59,0:05:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.59,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It bloomed...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Renato?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Mezarte?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.58,0:08:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.46,0:08:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Go alert the Elder!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.55,0:08:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.28,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They're attacking with Renato!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.08,0:08:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Protect the Hibiol!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.37,0:09:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like they say.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.62,0:09:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all a bunch of kids.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.91,0:09:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't they right inside your strike zone?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.67,0:09:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand down!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.54,0:09:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Izol.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.93,0:09:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your leader?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.61,0:09:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an honor to meet you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:50.49,0:09:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have heard that despite your youthful appearance, \Nyou are indeed a monster over four hundred years old.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.12,0:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Our lives consist of little more than weaving thread as we weave the days—just that simple repetition.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.46,0:10:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no reason for you to involve your—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.29,0:10:08.75,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,That is not your decision to make.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.92,0:10:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It is His Majesty's order.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.01,0:10:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You will accompany us to Mezarte's royal palace.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.89,0:10:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away from Elder Racine!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.89,0:10:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The women! Capture the women!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You have permission to cut down any who resist!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.62,0:10:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's come down with the Red-Eye!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:43.66,0:10:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ignore it! Prioritize the Iorph!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.34,0:10:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me out! Let me...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.46,0:11:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.12,0:12:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.78,0:13:24.53,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on, Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.53,0:13:25.87,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Jump on in!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.12,0:14:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.24,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, tear wine...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The saltiness gives it a real kick.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You lived with the Elder... Maquia, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.51,0:14:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on my way to buy Hibiol \Nwhen I got caught up here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.10,0:14:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a band of nomads, and by the looks of it, bandits did them in.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And boy, this one's fresh out of the oven.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.86,0:14:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta say though, mothers are real tough ones.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.40,0:14:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still trying to protect her kid in death.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.28,0:14:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she'll see him again soon enough in heaven.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.41,0:14:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,His Hibiol ends here.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.83,0:14:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a couple of threads, \Nnot even woven into cloth.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.88,0:14:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be better than growing up all alone at least.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.17,0:15:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he truly alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so... strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.71,0:15:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.00,0:15:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give it up already.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna take him with you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.81,0:15:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a toy—
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.85,0:15:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I know he's not a toy.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.02,0:15:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He's my...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:03.69,0:16:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hibiol.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.53,0:16:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief, what'll come of one lonesome connecting with another?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you cold?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.80,0:16:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell funny.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like sunshine.
