Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.44,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Try and get me, slowpoke!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:47.53,0:16:48.82,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,Get back here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.82,0:16:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lang! Deol! Quit slacking!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.41,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.99,0:16:56.83,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.83,0:16:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In your dreams!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.41,0:16:58.08,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,You little...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.08,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, those naughty brats...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.33,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it, Onora?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Boobies...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:21.06,0:17:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.10,0:17:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Boobies...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:23.90,0:17:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't un—
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.11,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.16,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Look here...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.99,0:17:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,A child can't possibly raise another child.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your baby?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell how old an Iorph is by her looks.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.93,0:17:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.35,0:17:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Lang, Deol.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.47,0:18:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm fifteen.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:01.73,0:18:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not... I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.24,0:18:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his name?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.75,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Weirdo.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Weird girl with a weird baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.46,0:18:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:27.63,0:18:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a girl's name. Isn't he a boy?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.51,0:18:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then Lei...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.97,0:18:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Li...liel...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.89,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.77,0:18:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, good enough.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.90,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a relative's kid, and she knows how to weave.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.37,0:19:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a loom in the back \Nnobody uses. You can have it.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.88,0:19:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait outside.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.18,0:19:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an Iorph.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.43,0:19:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing fools your eyes, Daryl.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.72,0:19:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.10,0:19:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Iorph cloth can fetch a high price.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:29.40,0:19:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't sell out a precious \Nsource of income to anyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.99,0:19:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.45,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, life was already tough enough for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.91,0:19:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're taking in this Iorph girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.49,0:19:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I get your point, but nobody knows \Nwhat tomorrow might bring.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.21,0:19:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Her being around isn't going change that.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.97,0:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, this week's delivery.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.88,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.18,0:20:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your farm's cheese has got something special about it...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.02,0:20:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You flatter me! I'll see you again next week.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.85,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Something out of the ordinary...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back every week this month!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.07,0:20:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real hair-puller trying to raise a kid alone, even for a woman like me.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.32,0:20:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.74,0:20:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I used to be married, but my husband was killed by a Renato with Red-Eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that all you can say?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.34,0:20:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what mothers are like, since I, well...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.60,0:20:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have one.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.77,0:20:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're like this!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.38,0:22:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He walked!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.18,0:22:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome, Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:04.80,0:22:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.18,0:22:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing! You're amazing, Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.32,0:22:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've got the face of a real mama now.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:23.49,0:22:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... a mama?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:27.37,0:22:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen a mom as unreliable as you!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.62,0:22:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you clean the goat shed like I asked?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.67,0:22:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Crud, it's Ma!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:34.79,0:22:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Huff it, Deol!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:35.92,0:22:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bark, bark!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.75,0:22:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ma!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.05,0:22:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're real sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:41.59,0:22:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:44.18,0:22:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:45.01,0:22:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Owwie!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.47,0:22:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Say "Mama".
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.73,0:22:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just kidding! I didn't mean it!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.73,0:22:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:00.82,0:23:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel, what did you just say?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.57,0:23:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:08.74,0:23:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Say it one more time.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.17,0:23:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Another Renato has contracted Red-Eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.09,0:23:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be euthanized at once.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.59,0:23:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We shall isolate and cremate its corpse, \Nand bury the remains deep underground.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:29.22,0:23:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There are now five remaining.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.68,0:23:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what tragedy!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:34.31,0:23:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezarte's reign over its neighboring countries
Dialogue: 10,0:23:38.27,0:23:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,is founded in the providence of \Nthe ancient wyverns, the Renato.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:41.78,0:23:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Should they become extinct, \Nthis fragile balance will collapse.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:46.49,0:23:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For Mezarte to maintain authority, we must acquire a substitute—
Dialogue: 10,0:23:50.49,0:23:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Something as equally fantastic as the Renato.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:53.20,0:23:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's it! We are already \Nin possession of the chosen bloodline!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:58.96,0:24:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Izor, what has become of that girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:02.17,0:24:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That Iorph who is to become the consort of Prince Hazel.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:07.72,0:24:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, tell me why.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:11.10,0:24:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You all have wings,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:14.31,0:24:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so why do you not fly away?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:22.40,0:24:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Scaredy-cats.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:24.86,0:24:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all going to die.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:27.74,0:24:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Your repressed feelings will burn your hearts, \Nturn your bodies to flame, and leave you in ashes.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:35.16,0:24:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:36.91,0:24:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,His Majesty summons you.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:39.71,0:24:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A moment.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:42.50,0:24:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia, what draws you here time and time again?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:47.05,0:24:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminds me of the Hibiol Tower.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:50.80,0:24:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:08.03,0:25:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished! Can you read it?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:10.57,0:25:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep! It says "Onora, get well soon."
Dialogue: 10,0:25:15.70,0:25:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In the place I was born, people would use weaving instead of writing to convey their feelings.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:21.79,0:25:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you were born? \NWhat about where I was born?
Dialogue: 10,0:25:26.71,0:25:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dita's mom said that you're different from them.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:33.05,0:25:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,In the place you were born,
Dialogue: 10,0:25:35.39,0:25:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,people talked with their tummies and the tickle bugs...
Dialogue: 10,0:25:39.56,0:25:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are! Tickle tickle tickle!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:41.35,0:25:44.11,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,But bellies only talk with farts!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:42.98,0:25:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whee!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:47.07,0:25:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Onora!
Dialogue: 10,0:25:48.94,0:25:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Lay it on him gently.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:55.53,0:25:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Onora.
Dialogue: 10,0:25:58.20,0:26:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Onora's been part of the family \Nsince Mom and Dad got married.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:02.25,0:26:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd be about ninety in human years by now.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:16.76,0:26:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom's so weird, Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:19.47,0:26:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always sneaking around everywhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:21.98,0:26:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not weird! My mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:24.98,0:26:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She... Mommy is—
Dialogue: 10,0:26:28.90,0:26:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He said "Mommy"!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:30.40,0:26:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a little baby!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:32.82,0:26:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the weird one, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:34.74,0:26:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:26:35.32,0:26:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys who love their moms are weird.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not weird! Mommy—
Dialogue: 10,0:26:41.41,0:26:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:26:42.25,0:26:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate her!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:43.75,0:26:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I love my mom.
Dialogue: 10,0:26:45.46,0:26:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:46.67,0:26:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hate you, Dita!
Dialogue: 10,0:26:55.55,0:26:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay, Dita?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:04.73,0:27:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is high quality.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:09.27,0:27:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, this month's pay.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:11.23,0:27:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I really appreciate it.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:12.94,0:27:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh right, I've got something \NI want you to take a look at.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:16.20,0:27:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Another client of mine brought in some Hibiol.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:18.78,0:27:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:30.88,0:27:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:32.34,0:27:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"At Mezarte Castle... marry the prince."
Dialogue: 10,0:27:37.68,0:27:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,"Beautiful..."
Dialogue: 10,0:27:40.31,0:27:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Lei...lia?
Dialogue: 10,0:27:42.93,0:27:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:27:46.64,0:27:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Daryl said he'll find a cargo ship \Nthat'll let you on board.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:51.86,0:27:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, that's her.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:53.15,0:27:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, this may have come at just the right time.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:53.86,0:27:55.11,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,She's creepy.
Dialogue: 10,0:27:57.82,0:28:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The only question is what to do about Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:00.33,0:28:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:28:01.83,0:28:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Taking a child on such a long journey will be more difficult than you can imagine.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:06.54,0:28:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially given your circumstances.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:11.29,0:28:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't mind looking after him.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:13.50,0:28:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom! Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:16.42,0:28:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:28:30.73,0:28:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, if you dig too deep, then if...
Dialogue: 10,0:28:34.44,0:28:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If Onora comes back to life—
Dialogue: 10,0:28:36.03,0:28:36.82,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:37.70,0:28:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's too shallow, the strays will dig him up.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:40.91,0:28:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:55.76,0:28:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see him with all the dirt on top.
Dialogue: 10,0:28:58.05,0:29:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be able to see him here anytime.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:00.97,0:29:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't play with him with all the dirt there.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:03.68,0:29:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him what a good boy he was.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:05.60,0:29:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He lived a good life, and passed away peacefully.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:10.31,0:29:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This day comes for us all.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:12.98,0:29:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Onora just happened to be born with a life that reached it before the rest of us.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:22.95,0:29:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:25.03,0:29:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:30.54,0:29:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:32.17,0:29:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Does everybody die?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:34.34,0:29:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:35.42,0:29:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:29:37.63,0:29:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:29:43.18,0:29:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:44.43,0:29:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:29:52.48,0:29:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:54.73,0:29:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone will...
Dialogue: 10,0:29:58.94,0:30:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll all reach that day... way, way before me!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:04.03,0:30:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:05.66,0:30:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I knew...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:08.33,0:30:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:12.46,0:30:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares about the order?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:16.59,0:30:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:19.38,0:30:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:22.05,0:30:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Ariel's mom, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:26.30,0:30:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Moms don't cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:28.72,0:30:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Even our mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:31.60,0:30:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that moms don't cry!
Dialogue: 10,0:30:39.15,0:30:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't cry...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:40.99,0:30:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, don't cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:44.95,0:30:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry...
Dialogue: 10,0:30:47.16,0:30:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm not crying.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:53.25,0:30:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good night.
Dialogue: 10,0:30:59.50,0:31:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:08.18,0:31:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you waiting for me?
Dialogue: 10,0:31:10.47,0:31:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get you to bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:19.11,0:31:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotten heavier.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:21.03,0:31:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:31:24.20,0:31:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You still smell like sunshine.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:26.95,0:31:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I won't cry.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:29.41,0:31:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'm your mom, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:32.45,0:31:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll always be together, forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:38.04,0:31:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I said that. I'm sorry \NI said that. I'm sorry I said that.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:47.09,0:31:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I said that. I'm sorry I said that.
Dialogue: 10,0:31:51.31,0:31:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel's not here anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:03.28,0:32:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you didn't \Nwant to see them off?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:22.92,0:32:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna go outside!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:24.13,0:32:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! I said you can't, Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:27.80,0:32:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, didn't you promise me?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:30.26,0:32:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here like a good boy.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:32.76,0:32:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:37.35,0:32:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia?
Dialogue: 10,0:32:42.06,0:32:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive, Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:44.36,0:32:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're alive, Krim!
Dialogue: 10,0:32:54.29,0:32:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezarte was after the long-lived blood of the Iorph.
Dialogue: 10,0:32:59.87,0:33:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they attacked the village... and took Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:04.21,0:33:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, who's Leilia?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:07.09,0:33:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making him call you "Mom"?
Dialogue: 10,0:33:10.30,0:33:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I'm not making him or anything...
Dialogue: 10,0:33:13.05,0:33:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not angry. I don't blame you.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:17.10,0:33:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just don't forget what the Elder always told us.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:22.15,0:33:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. I remember.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:25.53,0:33:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:33:58.10,0:34:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow morning, a parade will be held to celebrate the prince's marriage.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:03.02,0:34:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The Prince's procession will depart from the Royal Palace
Dialogue: 10,0:34:05.61,0:34:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and meet Leilia's procession from the detached palace at the bridge.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:10.03,0:34:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,At that point, we will attack the Prince's Renato,
Dialogue: 10,0:34:13.03,0:34:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,creating a disturbance, and weakening Leilia's escort.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:17.95,0:34:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we'll steal her back.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:21.66,0:34:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see the parade too.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:23.79,0:34:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, maybe next time.
Dialogue: 10,0:34:27.80,0:34:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mommy—
Dialogue: 10,0:34:29.51,0:34:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, I wanna go home!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:31.55,0:34:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel?
Dialogue: 10,0:34:34.09,0:34:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't act like mom when you're here!
Dialogue: 10,0:34:45.27,0:34:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel...
Dialogue: 10,0:34:46.77,0:34:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The tickle bugs... are here!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:25.94,0:35:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, we welcome Iorph blood into our royal bloodline!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:32.69,0:35:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The Renato and the Iorph!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:34.95,0:35:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We have acquired two ancient legends that live on in the modern age!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:41.62,0:35:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,As God's chosen ones, none can stand against us!
Dialogue: 10,0:35:51.55,0:35:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And with the consummation of \NPrince Hazel and Princess Leilia's marriage,
Dialogue: 10,0:35:56.68,0:36:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,a new legend will be born in Mezarte!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:15.55,0:37:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That man!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:31.69,0:37:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an assassin?
Dialogue: 10,0:37:32.98,0:37:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:41.95,0:37:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia! Leilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:37:53.17,0:37:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops! Sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:02.51,0:38:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:06.31,0:38:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia... Why are you here?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:10.18,0:38:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Krim is here too.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:12.94,0:38:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Krim is...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:14.15,0:38:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:15.69,0:38:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone is waiting for...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:18.07,0:38:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:20.40,0:38:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go anymore.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:23.36,0:38:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:38:25.78,0:38:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't escape.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:27.87,0:38:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! You've always been fast.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:30.83,0:38:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! You could even fly \Nfrom the top of the castle...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:44.43,0:38:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never face Krim again.
Dialogue: 10,0:38:48.93,0:38:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not... you can't...
Dialogue: 10,0:38:51.60,0:38:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:54.81,0:38:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:56.81,0:38:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But Leilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:38:59.23,0:39:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! I'll be fine. You know I can fly.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:03.78,0:39:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Capture them!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:16.46,0:39:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:18.92,0:39:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After them!
Dialogue: 10,0:39:19.42,0:39:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:20.63,0:39:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If you lay a finger on her...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:33.60,0:39:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia...
Dialogue: 10,0:39:42.99,0:39:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I can... fly.
Dialogue: 10,0:39:53.75,0:39:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Has the baby grown up?
Dialogue: 10,0:39:56.67,0:39:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Should be around six, if he's still alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:00.50,0:40:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the world treating you?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:04.59,0:40:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're an Iorph too?
Dialogue: 10,0:40:07.05,0:40:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just half.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:09.30,0:40:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Racine... The Elder made it taboo \Nfor Iorph to leave the village
Dialogue: 10,0:40:16.81,0:40:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,because she knows exactly \Nwhat awaits those who do so.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:22.19,0:40:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what, as long as you're different, people will avoid you, use you,
Dialogue: 10,0:40:28.41,0:40:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and eventually come to revile and reject you.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:32.24,0:40:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So you see, the Clan of Partings is doomed to live up to its name.
Dialogue: 10,0:40:43.17,0:40:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good life.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:04.40,0:41:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Krim, you're hurt.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:12.45,0:41:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take off your cloak?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:19.50,0:41:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What's it like... having a baby?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:23.84,0:41:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean to be a mother?
Dialogue: 10,0:41:28.63,0:41:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I'm a mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:34.10,0:41:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mido taught me what I didn't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:38.48,0:41:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She helped me a lot, \Nso he felt like a younger brother.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:43.40,0:41:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet... it's kind of different.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:47.36,0:41:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,When Ariel laughs, I feel so happy.
Dialogue: 10,0:41:51.99,0:41:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why if me being there will make him smile,
Dialogue: 10,0:41:57.37,0:42:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be with him forev—
Dialogue: 10,0:41:59.37,0:42:01.00,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,You say some funny things.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:04.08,0:42:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to die before you.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:08.26,0:42:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel is going to leave you alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:17.22,0:42:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make her cry!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:18.52,0:42:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,He wasn't, Ariel! Krim was just...
Dialogue: 10,0:42:19.14,0:42:21.98,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,Don't make Mommy cry!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:21.98,0:42:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel, stop that!
Dialogue: 10,0:42:24.44,0:42:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you protect it?
Dialogue: 10,0:42:27.48,0:42:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's most precious to you.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:51.80,0:42:55.55,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,We will stay in Mezarte and rescue Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:42:56.39,0:42:58.93,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,You're only a hindrance with your child here.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:00.10,0:43:02.39,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,So, Maquia,
Dialogue: 10,0:43:03.19,0:43:04.48,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:07.27,0:43:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we going home?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:09.78,0:43:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be going home.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:12.28,0:43:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What about everyone else?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:15.53,0:43:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me will be going to a new place.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:19.41,0:43:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A new place without Mido or Lang or Deol?
Dialogue: 10,0:43:25.79,0:43:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it looks like that was our last goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:30.59,0:43:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,All I need is you!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:35.05,0:43:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And Mom doesn't need anyone but you, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:39.05,0:43:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:40.64,0:43:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell you've got some kind of baggage.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:42.56,0:43:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I ain't gonna risk you making trouble and running off from under my nose.
Dialogue: 10,0:43:49.11,0:43:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:50.94,0:43:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:53.28,0:43:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, get back here you brats!
Dialogue: 10,0:43:57.28,0:44:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom needs to go check out a few \Nmore places, so stay put in our room here.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:02.12,0:44:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I don't wanna.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:04.16,0:44:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait here for me, please.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:11.84,0:44:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:13.67,0:44:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We mainly serve drinks here, so you'll be getting lots of late-night shifts.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:18.30,0:44:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:19.97,0:44:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Late-night shifts?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:22.22,0:44:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That a problem?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:24.85,0:44:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,My child is, um... very young.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:30.94,0:44:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Great, same as the last girl who quit.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:33.86,0:44:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You must all have dirt for brains \Nto get knocked up so young.
Dialogue: 10,0:44:36.86,0:44:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not—
Dialogue: 10,0:44:38.20,0:44:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not? Not what?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:40.53,0:44:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Aware of what it means to be a real mother?
Dialogue: 10,0:44:44.04,0:44:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't have any work \NI could rely on you for.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:04.22,0:45:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:07.43,0:45:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:11.23,0:45:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, lookie, lookie! The Hibiol...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:20.36,0:45:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make more work for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:22.37,0:45:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:23.70,0:45:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you take this out?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:28.46,0:45:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at it, Mom—
Dialogue: 10,0:45:30.29,0:45:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you listen to me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:32.83,0:45:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... You did it earlier too.
Dialogue: 10,0:45:35.88,0:45:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't work, we won't have any food to eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:40.51,0:45:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:41.39,0:45:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this to me?
Dialogue: 10,0:45:44.60,0:45:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:46.68,0:45:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The tickle bugs are here!
Dialogue: 10,0:45:49.43,0:45:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tickle tickle tickle...
Dialogue: 10,0:45:52.94,0:45:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought dinner.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:00.11,0:46:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:46:09.58,0:46:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm no mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:46:13.00,0:46:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly be a real mother?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:18.26,0:46:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just pretending...
Dialogue: 10,0:46:21.84,0:46:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only because Mido was there...
Dialogue: 10,0:46:24.55,0:46:26.76,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,You mustn't fall in love.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:26.76,0:46:30.77,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,If you love, you will become truly alone.
Dialogue: 10,0:46:32.06,0:46:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly... alone?
Dialogue: 10,0:46:49.41,0:46:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,"M-o-m."
Dialogue: 10,0:46:53.62,0:46:54.79,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:09.51,0:47:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:15.81,0:47:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel?
Dialogue: 10,0:47:19.02,0:47:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Ariel?!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:25.11,0:47:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:26.20,0:47:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:28.41,0:47:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:35.83,0:47:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I fooled you!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:38.17,0:47:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought I shed my skin!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:46.51,0:47:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Shed your skin? Come on...
Dialogue: 10,0:47:47.84,0:47:49.35,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,You laughed!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:50.97,0:47:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:47:55.52,0:47:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Dummy.
Dialogue: 10,0:47:58.11,0:47:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 10,0:48:00.36,0:48:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you never had to grow any bigger.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:06.32,0:48:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:09.70,0:48:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't get bigger, I can't protect you!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:18.54,0:48:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You cried again.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:22.59,0:48:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't cry!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:24.34,0:48:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your mom, after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:48:30.18,0:48:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:31.76,0:48:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:41.73,0:48:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel, you promise too.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:44.15,0:48:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:48:46.32,0:48:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:30.57,0:49:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Grub's up.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:32.37,0:49:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:33.99,0:49:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:37.54,0:49:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't think I've forgotten about the favor you owe me.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:41.00,0:49:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, you're just bragging about your woman.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:43.25,0:49:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say jack! Screw you!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:46.59,0:49:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll learn this angle through experience.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:53.85,0:49:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I told you to quit while you're ahead!
Dialogue: 10,0:49:56.31,0:49:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure it'd work out this time.
Dialogue: 10,0:49:59.14,0:50:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:04.81,0:50:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia, three kelbeers!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:07.07,0:50:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:09.40,0:50:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,On the way!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:10.36,0:50:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Get us a refill too.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:11.70,0:50:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:14.07,0:50:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister's got a nice ass.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:17.41,0:50:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 10,0:50:19.83,0:50:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta say though, I can't see the resemblance.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:23.38,0:50:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So,
Dialogue: 10,0:50:24.71,0:50:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,you've been here for almost a year.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:28.63,0:50:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Where were you before?
Dialogue: 10,0:50:31.72,0:50:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we were just thinking that maybe you're not really siblings, but a couple that eloped.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:38.06,0:50:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:40.77,0:50:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:45.06,0:50:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 10,0:50:49.90,0:50:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Another new group.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:52.11,0:50:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How many guards do they need \Nto send before they're satisfied?
Dialogue: 10,0:50:55.12,0:50:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, iron's hot right now.
Dialogue: 10,0:50:57.99,0:51:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Mezarte ordering so many weapons, we can all keep food on our plates.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:21.81,0:51:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's definitely something brewing.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:24.56,0:51:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they getting ready to start a war?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:27.23,0:51:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You really think that dimwitted prince can lead an army?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:30.36,0:51:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:37.62,0:51:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:39.62,0:51:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize for all the noise. \NThis is today's menu.
Dialogue: 10,0:51:54.09,0:51:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,0:51:55.38,0:51:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Lang?
Dialogue: 10,0:51:58.47,0:52:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it had to be you, Maquia! \NYou haven't changed at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:01.47,0:52:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess that's obvious.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:02.81,0:52:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You've really changed!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:04.77,0:52:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get so big?
Dialogue: 10,0:52:07.10,0:52:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't treat me like a beanstalk.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:11.27,0:52:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:13.53,0:52:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:15.53,0:52:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Lang! Your big brother Lang!
Dialogue: 10,0:52:18.57,0:52:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! {\i1}You're{\i0} Ariel?
Dialogue: 10,0:52:31.84,0:52:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't mind me coming?
Dialogue: 10,0:52:33.42,0:52:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I'm sorry it's so messy.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:36.55,0:52:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really glad to hear that \NMido and Deol are doing well.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:40.26,0:52:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but business is only \Nbooming in cities like Dreil.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:44.77,0:52:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,All the rural areas are slowly drying up.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:47.73,0:52:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Deol left home to—Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:50.44,0:52:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Deol went to find work too?
Dialogue: 10,0:52:52.61,0:52:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't survive otherwise.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:55.03,0:52:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to leave.
Dialogue: 10,0:52:58.36,0:53:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's this? Got a hot date tonight?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:01.37,0:53:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a night shift.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:05.08,0:53:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:07.29,0:53:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll prepare a light meal.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:09.71,0:53:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:18.72,0:53:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He got a job once we moved here... \NHe's working so hard for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:24.10,0:53:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:25.72,0:53:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't exactly go around selling Hibiol, you know?
Dialogue: 10,0:53:28.52,0:53:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And because of me, we can't even \Nstay in one place for long.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:35.86,0:53:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:38.45,0:53:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And he must've realized by now that you're not related by blood.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:45.29,0:53:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It was about five years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:48.75,0:53:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,When he suddenly asked to have his own bed.
Dialogue: 10,0:53:52.25,0:53:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now he doesn't even call me Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:53:56.13,0:54:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just "Hey!" or "Over here!" \Nwhenever he wants my attention.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:00.84,0:54:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just a phase. \NI went through the same thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:04.72,0:54:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Lang.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:06.97,0:54:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what happened to Leilia?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:19.32,0:54:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Another dead...
Dialogue: 10,0:54:23.70,0:54:27.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Cremate it down to the bones and be sure to bury the ashes deep underground.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:30.16,0:54:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:31.50,0:54:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no need to fear, Miss Medmel.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:34.04,0:54:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, where is Father?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:35.96,0:54:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Hazel has duties to attend to.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:41.05,0:54:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What about Mo...
Dialogue: 10,0:54:43.18,0:54:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Medmel?
Dialogue: 10,0:54:47.31,0:54:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:50.27,0:54:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hair the hue of a daybreak moon, a golden ring around the pupils,
Dialogue: 10,0:54:54.35,0:54:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention the low body temperature characteristic of the Iorph.
Dialogue: 10,0:54:57.98,0:55:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Medmel does not display a single one of these physical traits.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:01.86,0:55:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be! If she cannot bear a son and pass on her long life, why do we keep that monster around?
Dialogue: 10,0:55:10.58,0:55:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears she cannot bear any more children after Miss Medmel.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:13.67,0:55:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that Prince Hazel seems to have tired of Lady Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:17.67,0:55:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, my poor son Hazel!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:21.30,0:55:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something about this!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:22.59,0:55:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At least find him a new woman!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:25.68,0:55:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course. We will find another Iorph survivor to use as a surrogate mother.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:32.31,0:55:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand it!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:33.31,0:55:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:35.85,0:55:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You dress and decorate me like a jewelry box, and still he refuses to sleep with me...
Dialogue: 10,0:55:40.86,0:55:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So just throw me out already!
Dialogue: 10,0:55:48.03,0:55:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia is...
Dialogue: 10,0:55:49.20,0:55:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I will handle her.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:56.83,0:55:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So another Renato died.
Dialogue: 10,0:55:59.21,0:55:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:01.34,0:56:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since giving birth to Medmel,
Dialogue: 10,0:56:04.34,0:56:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been locked up in here.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:08.09,0:56:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even permitted to see her.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:12.47,0:56:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure... the Renato and I are the same.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:17.44,0:56:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncertain existences that can only \Nlive in the fogs of legend.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:23.36,0:56:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither those who flew the skies nor flowers that sang at dawn can survive in this world.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:31.33,0:56:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You should still be able to resist.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:33.95,0:56:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And find a way to save the legends.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:39.13,0:56:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk.
Dialogue: 10,0:56:41.84,0:56:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,After {\i1}you{\i0} killed our legend with your own two hands!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:04.53,0:57:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Please allow me to atone.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:07.03,0:57:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck you!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:09.24,0:57:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let me see Medmel!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:12.20,0:57:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why won't you bring me to her?
Dialogue: 10,0:57:14.79,0:57:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my flesh and blood!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:17.91,0:57:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already begun to forget her scent.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:23.13,0:57:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The softness of her touch...
Dialogue: 10,0:57:26.88,0:57:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... How much more do you want to take from me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:32.93,0:57:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you... want me to be alone that badly?
Dialogue: 10,0:57:38.98,0:57:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can't see Medmel, then bring Maquia here!
Dialogue: 10,0:57:47.15,0:57:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please... bring me Maquia the Iorph.
Dialogue: 10,0:57:51.57,0:57:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't... want to be alone anymore!
Dialogue: 10,0:58:07.55,0:58:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being rather thorough.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:09.55,0:58:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always been just the two of us, right? I wasn't prepared to entertain a guest.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:19.35,0:58:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, could I get a hand?
Dialogue: 10,0:58:21.23,0:58:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:31.03,0:58:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've grown taller again.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:33.11,0:58:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't sound so surprised.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:40.46,0:58:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia, we need to talk.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:42.83,0:58:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you come see me after work?
Dialogue: 10,0:58:44.83,0:58:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Sure, but it'll be a while...
Dialogue: 10,0:58:46.84,0:58:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hang around until you're done.
Dialogue: 10,0:58:49.21,0:58:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia, come deliver this!
Dialogue: 10,0:58:51.13,0:58:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:58:57.60,0:59:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all laying off cause \Nwe thought she was your girl.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:01.14,0:59:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, seriously.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:02.81,0:59:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of good men here to pick from already, ain't there?
Dialogue: 10,0:59:07.19,0:59:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't believe she got scooped up by that guy.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:09.40,0:59:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:12.03,0:59:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:59:13.49,0:59:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheer up, fellas.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:15.57,0:59:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, have a drink.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:16.91,0:59:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not...
Dialogue: 10,0:59:18.62,0:59:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a kid, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:59:26.00,0:59:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty good. Let's see you handle this one now.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:30.71,0:59:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on becoming a man.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:33.17,0:59:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If! If! If! If! If you're a man...
Dialogue: 10,0:59:37.22,0:59:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Melt it down! Bang it up! Melt it down! Bang it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:41.31,0:59:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Chug! Chug! Chug! Chug!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:44.81,0:59:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:46.90,0:59:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not half bad!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:48.27,0:59:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get you another!
Dialogue: 10,0:59:50.27,0:59:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us your manliness.
Dialogue: 10,0:59:56.99,0:59:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're looking for me?
Dialogue: 10,1:00:01.12,1:00:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we'll have to skip town.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:04.46,1:00:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you return to the farm with me?
Dialogue: 10,1:00:07.88,1:00:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,1:00:08.71,1:00:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it work! The price of \Ngoat milk's gone up too.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:12.51,1:00:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll bring Ariel too.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:14.34,1:00:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't impose like that.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:16.30,1:00:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,1:00:17.59,1:00:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If I ended up bringing trouble to \NMido or Deol's doorstep, I...
Dialogue: 10,1:00:24.60,1:00:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I...
Dialogue: 10,1:00:26.69,1:00:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to impose.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:29.61,1:00:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since I was a kid, \NI've wanted to be there for you.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:35.86,1:00:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it, Maquia.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:38.87,1:00:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,About your future.
Dialogue: 10,1:00:40.41,1:00:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 10,1:00:43.49,1:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,About me.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:01.85,1:01:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I can even consider it.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:06.48,1:01:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've only ever thought about Ariel before.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:11.86,1:01:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How I can keep on living with Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:16.11,1:01:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How I can be like a real mother.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:20.41,1:01:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've never been able to find an answer.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:25.87,1:01:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I don't think I'm close to one either.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:32.46,1:01:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not very smart, so...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:36.38,1:01:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to continue to think only about Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:48.60,1:01:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:50.60,1:01:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Still...
Dialogue: 10,1:01:52.19,1:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,At least let me help you figure out \Nwhere to move and find work.
Dialogue: 10,1:01:57.24,1:01:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bear the burden yourself.
Dialogue: 10,1:02:30.39,1:02:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel?
Dialogue: 10,1:02:36.07,1:02:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you doing out here?
Dialogue: 10,1:02:38.86,1:02:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You smell like alcohol.
Dialogue: 10,1:02:40.61,1:02:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back...
Dialogue: 10,1:02:41.86,1:02:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for that! \NWhat happened to you, Ariel?
Dialogue: 10,1:02:44.74,1:02:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's my welcome home kiss?
Dialogue: 10,1:02:47.20,1:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You always... used to do it when I got back.
Dialogue: 10,1:02:54.88,1:02:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 10,1:02:56.50,1:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, can you stand?
Dialogue: 10,1:02:59.05,1:03:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They thought... we had eloped together...
Dialogue: 10,1:03:05.72,1:03:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That you were being taken by another man...
Dialogue: 10,1:03:09.64,1:03:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:11.31,1:03:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, get up!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:13.39,1:03:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to sleep in bed—
Dialogue: 10,1:03:25.11,1:03:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you make it by yourself?
Dialogue: 10,1:03:33.83,1:03:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't step on it!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:42.09,1:03:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 10,1:03:44.59,1:03:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the one who wove it for me.
Dialogue: 10,1:03:52.60,1:03:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate it...
Dialogue: 10,1:03:56.15,1:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you still keeping this?!
Dialogue: 10,1:03:59.40,1:04:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop treating me like a child!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:29.60,1:04:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll never change.
Dialogue: 10,1:04:35.60,1:04:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my treasure.
Dialogue: 10,1:04:41.40,1:04:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,1:04:47.82,1:04:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Ariel. We're going to have to move again.
Dialogue: 10,1:04:54.25,1:04:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want to go next?
Dialogue: 10,1:04:56.25,1:04:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere's fine with me.
Dialogue: 10,1:04:59.63,1:05:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as we're together.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:02.80,1:05:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,1:05:04.55,1:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think of you as my mother.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:32.74,1:05:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you put in a good word for me to be hired to the royal guard?
Dialogue: 10,1:05:41.21,1:05:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:43.38,1:05:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make Maquia sad.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:45.80,1:05:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not my real mother.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:48.92,1:05:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say that?
Dialogue: 10,1:05:52.09,1:05:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say that to Maquia?
Dialogue: 10,1:05:54.81,1:05:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 10,1:05:57.73,1:06:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think she went through, how she felt, as she raised you?!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:03.69,1:06:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Grow up already!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:05.27,1:06:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia's been desperately trying to become a mother since she was your age!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:10.03,1:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And you—
Dialogue: 10,1:06:10.99,1:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't understand!
Dialogue: 10,1:06:14.95,1:06:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does she care about me so much?
Dialogue: 10,1:06:23.63,1:06:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel...
Dialogue: 10,1:06:25.00,1:06:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always been by my side...
Dialogue: 10,1:06:27.92,1:06:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd do anything for me...
Dialogue: 10,1:06:31.30,1:06:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that was what made someone a mother.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:35.51,1:06:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I called her Mom.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:41.35,1:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to protect her.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:46.73,1:06:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't protect her as I am now.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:50.82,1:06:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even worse...
Dialogue: 10,1:06:53.86,1:06:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurt her.
Dialogue: 10,1:06:56.20,1:06:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally realized why I act this way.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:00.83,1:07:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I can't protect her!
Dialogue: 10,1:07:16.43,1:07:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Seeing you cry like this makes it seem like you're still the baby you used to be.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:25.52,1:07:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 10,1:07:47.63,1:07:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, I can do that myself.
Dialogue: 10,1:07:50.21,1:07:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have to pack too?
Dialogue: 10,1:07:52.72,1:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,After I see you off.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:07.02,1:08:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful out there, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:11.94,1:08:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:18.70,1:08:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:56.32,1:08:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't... cry.
Dialogue: 10,1:08:58.45,1:08:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't cry.
Dialogue: 10,1:09:00.32,1:09:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised.
Dialogue: 10,1:09:05.66,1:09:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:09:08.71,1:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to protect...
Dialogue: 10,1:09:14.25,1:09:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You lied...
Dialogue: 10,1:09:17.84,1:09:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,1:10:32.42,1:10:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Darn, I was hoping to see a real Renato.
Dialogue: 10,1:10:36.92,1:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't blame them. \NThere used to be a lot long ago,
Dialogue: 10,1:10:40.26,1:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but now there's only one left at the castle.
Dialogue: 10,1:10:44.51,1:10:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to have a parade with this arts-and-crafts Renato won't do a lick for raising soldier morale.
Dialogue: 10,1:10:50.43,1:10:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, did you hear?
Dialogue: 10,1:10:52.35,1:10:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently Vaiella got themselves an Iorph.
Dialogue: 10,1:10:55.11,1:10:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Vaiella? No kidding?
Dialogue: 10,1:11:00.36,1:11:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General, please don't burn your lice there.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:04.49,1:11:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:05.82,1:11:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General Lang!
Dialogue: 10,1:11:10.83,1:11:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're on the lookout.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:13.54,1:11:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's supposed to be a girl who looks the same age as Princess Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:19.21,1:11:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no guarantee it's Maquia.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:22.17,1:11:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You worried?
Dialogue: 10,1:11:24.13,1:11:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No... She's strong.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:29.01,1:11:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia would be thrilled to hear that.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:32.39,1:11:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She could never get away from worrying about whether she could protect you, and yet she soldiered on.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:39.82,1:11:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted you to view her as a \Nrespectable mom you could rely on.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:46.49,1:11:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What a kid.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:51.54,1:11:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... she was a kid.
Dialogue: 10,1:11:55.33,1:11:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,1:11:56.21,1:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be a father.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:07.22,1:12:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezarte is a paper tiger.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:10.72,1:12:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In an act of foolish sacrilege, they have turned ancient legends into military might.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:17.31,1:12:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do everything in our power to assist you.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:41.13,1:12:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:42.96,1:12:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're finally ready.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:46.63,1:12:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair's grown long.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:48.68,1:12:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The Iorph are only allowed to grow their hair past the waist after giving birth to a child.
Dialogue: 10,1:12:54.02,1:12:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Maquia. It is time to reclaim Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:06.49,1:13:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it become a war?
Dialogue: 10,1:13:08.53,1:13:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It only hurts for a moment.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:11.41,1:13:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've been bearing far greater pain over these last few years.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:16.54,1:13:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You left Iorph, lost everything you ever held dear, \Nand lived in some hole in the ground like a corpse.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:24.80,1:13:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,1:13:26.72,1:13:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you finally understand how we felt?
Dialogue: 10,1:13:29.76,1:13:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all separated, \Nand I doubt the Elder is still alive.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:36.22,1:13:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost everything and suffered for it.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:39.69,1:13:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet all the while, only you were living happily.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:45.23,1:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The people of Iorph work together to weave a single cloth.
Dialogue: 10,1:13:49.15,1:13:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You, me, and Leilia... our pasts must not be different.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:05.05,1:14:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Maquia.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:06.92,1:14:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now your exclusive past has disappeared.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:10.51,1:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all weave a single future again.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:35.99,1:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Dita!
Dialogue: 10,1:14:38.41,1:14:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:45.50,1:14:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back early today.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:47.92,1:14:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I have to run about \Nat such an important time.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:51.76,1:14:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,They said it'll still be a while before it's time.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:54.93,1:14:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:55.85,1:14:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I just can't help but worry.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:58.22,1:14:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dinner will be ready soon.
Dialogue: 10,1:14:59.98,1:15:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, you just relax. I'll bring it over.
Dialogue: 10,1:15:03.69,1:15:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm supposed to move at least a little.
Dialogue: 10,1:15:07.73,1:15:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, sit down already.
Dialogue: 10,1:15:10.36,1:15:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,1:15:14.87,1:15:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We've come so far. It feels almost magical.
Dialogue: 10,1:15:17.78,1:15:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,1:15:19.20,1:15:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I came out to Mezarte looking for work, and saw you again after all these years.
Dialogue: 10,1:15:26.54,1:15:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 10,1:15:30.21,1:15:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:15:32.38,1:15:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I really the right girl for you?
Dialogue: 10,1:15:38.93,1:15:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,1:16:06.37,1:16:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Vaiella?
Dialogue: 10,1:16:07.42,1:16:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Those aren't just Vaiellan ships.
Dialogue: 10,1:16:09.92,1:16:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's Jugh and Endora too!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:18.51,1:16:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel, wait!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:21.31,1:16:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You protect our child!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:41.87,1:16:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:16:43.04,1:16:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My apologies!
Dialogue: 10,1:16:51.17,1:16:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We have reports that the \NVaiella army has crossed the pass.
Dialogue: 10,1:16:54.97,1:16:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Split into two—
Dialogue: 10,1:17:01.51,1:17:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,How ironic.
Dialogue: 10,1:17:10.36,1:17:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezarte exploited ancient powers to put on a display of strength.
Dialogue: 10,1:17:16.44,1:17:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But as a result, the neighboring countries have decided to pass judgement on our abuse of those very powers
Dialogue: 10,1:17:22.08,1:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,and have combined forces to punish us.
Dialogue: 10,1:17:35.38,1:17:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are my ministers?!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:37.30,1:17:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They have apparently already escaped the castle with their retainers.
Dialogue: 10,1:17:41.80,1:17:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to say they have betrayed me?
Dialogue: 10,1:17:43.97,1:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What has the world come to?!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:46.81,1:17:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over! This is goodbye...
Dialogue: 10,1:17:50.90,1:17:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty, please make haste.
Dialogue: 10,1:17:52.98,1:17:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Miss Medmel?
Dialogue: 10,1:17:56.28,1:17:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not speak that accursed name. \NI have no need for it!
Dialogue: 10,1:17:59.07,1:18:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Abandon it along with the mother!
Dialogue: 10,1:18:51.62,1:18:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia, let's go!
Dialogue: 10,1:19:28.83,1:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,1:19:32.46,1:19:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel!
Dialogue: 10,1:19:51.39,1:19:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia...
Dialogue: 10,1:19:53.98,1:19:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you at last.
Dialogue: 10,1:19:57.86,1:19:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Krim?
Dialogue: 10,1:20:00.44,1:20:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 10,1:20:02.90,1:20:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You were alive?
Dialogue: 10,1:20:05.16,1:20:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I seeing...
Dialogue: 10,1:20:11.33,1:20:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,...a ghost?
Dialogue: 10,1:20:17.88,1:20:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come for you.
Dialogue: 10,1:20:20.75,1:20:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hurt those who harmed you countless times over.
Dialogue: 10,1:20:28.09,1:20:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I'll wipe everything clean—
Dialogue: 10,1:20:30.85,1:20:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 10,1:20:35.14,1:20:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to see her... My daughter.
Dialogue: 10,1:20:40.52,1:20:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 10,1:20:42.69,1:20:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't she forced onto you? \NA child you never wanted?
Dialogue: 10,1:20:46.28,1:20:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I gave birth to her...
Dialogue: 10,1:20:48.62,1:20:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You can forget about her!
Dialogue: 10,1:20:50.24,1:20:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter's name isn't etched into your Hibiol.
Dialogue: 10,1:20:53.58,1:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 10,1:20:56.50,1:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you and the others were dead...
Dialogue: 10,1:21:02.00,1:21:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And I...
Dialogue: 10,1:21:09.72,1:21:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I had lost everything...
Dialogue: 10,1:21:13.72,1:21:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've kept only my daughter in my thoughts...
Dialogue: 10,1:21:19.65,1:21:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That I want to see her...
Dialogue: 10,1:21:23.90,1:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That I want to hold her...
Dialogue: 10,1:21:27.15,1:21:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've managed to stay alive on just those feelings...
Dialogue: 10,1:21:33.79,1:21:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,1:21:37.75,1:21:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,My... Medmel...
Dialogue: 10,1:21:54.56,1:21:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,1:21:58.94,1:22:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end it all here, together.
Dialogue: 10,1:22:05.78,1:22:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Krim?
Dialogue: 10,1:22:12.41,1:22:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't...
Dialogue: 10,1:22:18.79,1:22:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...allow anyone else...
Dialogue: 10,1:22:23.13,1:22:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...to dirty our Hibiol any further.
Dialogue: 10,1:22:35.22,1:22:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Krim?
Dialogue: 10,1:22:40.02,1:22:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia!
Dialogue: 10,1:23:13.55,1:23:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Why...
Dialogue: 10,1:23:15.97,1:23:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Leilia and Maquia... why?
Dialogue: 10,1:23:21.89,1:23:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... did their time keep moving?
Dialogue: 10,1:24:03.98,1:24:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just like that day...
Dialogue: 10,1:24:33.17,1:24:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:24:35.84,1:24:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Major General.
Dialogue: 10,1:24:37.72,1:24:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We've received word of an Iorph boy and girl aboard the Vaiellan ships.
Dialogue: 10,1:24:44.77,1:24:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did you see her?
Dialogue: 10,1:24:49.02,1:24:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,1:24:50.94,1:24:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done here. Leave this post \Nto us and go find Maquia—
Dialogue: 10,1:24:54.15,1:24:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will fight!
Dialogue: 10,1:24:56.40,1:24:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you really that loyal to Mezarte?
Dialogue: 10,1:24:59.20,1:25:02.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Surely not. You simply wanted \Nto run away from Ma—
Dialogue: 10,1:25:02.41,1:25:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 10,1:25:04.70,1:25:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right that I thought that way at first.
Dialogue: 10,1:25:07.83,1:25:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, I have Dita.
Dialogue: 10,1:25:11.17,1:25:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I have my comrades.
Dialogue: 10,1:25:12.88,1:25:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a baby on the way too.
Dialogue: 10,1:25:15.84,1:25:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Mezarte is the first home \NI made after I left her side.
Dialogue: 10,1:25:21.51,1:25:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to protect it!
Dialogue: 10,1:25:43.66,1:25:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,1:25:51.17,1:25:52.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 10,1:25:52.00,1:25:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,A doctor!
Dialogue: 10,1:25:53.21,1:25:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 10,1:25:55.59,1:25:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Not now...
Dialogue: 10,1:25:57.26,1:25:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 10,1:26:00.43,1:26:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... Ariel's child!
Dialogue: 10,1:26:10.27,1:26:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 10,1:26:31.79,1:26:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 10,1:26:36.96,1:26:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dita...
Dialogue: 10,1:26:39.59,1:26:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it. Almost there!
Dialogue: 10,1:26:42.59,1:26:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll get to meet your baby.
Dialogue: 10,1:27:04.87,1:27:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it, you're doing great!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:07.62,1:27:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dita, just a little more.
Dialogue: 10,1:27:11.54,1:27:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're almost there!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:14.50,1:27:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dita!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:22.43,1:27:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Attack!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:33.19,1:27:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm scared!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:35.77,1:27:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Dita!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:36.44,1:27:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared... I'm scared! Help me!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:39.90,1:27:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Dita, you'll be okay—
Dialogue: 10,1:27:41.11,1:27:42.36,Default Alt,,0,0,0,,The baby!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:42.36,1:27:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save my baby!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:45.66,1:27:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 10,1:27:47.91,1:27:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We will!
Dialogue: 10,1:27:51.50,1:27:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Dawn is coming! Stay on the attack!
Dialogue: 10,1:28:09.76,1:28:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, it's your baby! It's yearning to be born!
Dialogue: 10,1:28:15.90,1:28:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You and Ariel are going to be a mom and dad!
Dialogue: 10,1:28:51.81,1:28:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You did so well, Dita.
Dialogue: 10,1:28:55.14,1:28:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom.
Dialogue: 10,1:29:14.25,1:29:16.66,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,You gonna take him with you?
Dialogue: 10,1:29:16.66,1:29:17.79,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,He's not a toy—
Dialogue: 10,1:29:17.79,1:29:19.33,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I know he's not a toy.
Dialogue: 10,1:29:19.33,1:29:20.67,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,He's my...
Dialogue: 10,1:29:21.46,1:29:22.92,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Hibiol.
Dialogue: 10,1:29:25.76,1:29:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,1:29:29.09,1:29:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,1:29:41.31,1:29:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel! It's time to come inside!
Dialogue: 10,1:29:44.86,1:29:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,1:29:46.82,1:29:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 10,1:29:52.03,1:29:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Look how cold you are.
Dialogue: 10,1:29:57.04,1:29:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:30:06.76,1:30:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 10,1:30:10.34,1:30:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:30:15.22,1:30:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 10,1:30:16.93,1:30:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a dream.
Dialogue: 10,1:30:19.39,1:30:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But... it's snowing...
Dialogue: 10,1:30:22.48,1:30:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not snow. It's ash.
Dialogue: 10,1:30:36.83,1:30:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your baby with Dita was born.
Dialogue: 10,1:30:43.25,1:30:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 10,1:30:44.88,1:30:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. They're waiting for you.
Dialogue: 10,1:30:48.30,1:30:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll wait for you as long as it takes.
Dialogue: 10,1:30:53.72,1:30:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how your mother \Nmust've given birth to you.
Dialogue: 10,1:31:04.52,1:31:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,When I found you, your mom was holding on to you so tightly.
Dialogue: 10,1:31:12.15,1:31:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Her fingers clung stiffly around you.
Dialogue: 10,1:31:15.74,1:31:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a hard time getting you out.
Dialogue: 10,1:31:19.04,1:31:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,One finger, then another...
Dialogue: 10,1:31:21.87,1:31:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough—
Dialogue: 10,1:31:22.79,1:31:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad...
Dialogue: 10,1:31:25.08,1:31:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't able to become your mom—
Dialogue: 10,1:31:28.13,1:31:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop!
Dialogue: 10,1:31:31.80,1:31:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You taught me so much.
Dialogue: 10,1:31:34.30,1:31:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Kindness, strength, dedication...
Dialogue: 10,1:31:39.68,1:31:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What it means to love someone.
Dialogue: 10,1:31:47.86,1:31:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about your well-being...
Dialogue: 10,1:31:50.99,1:31:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It felt like I was thinking about my own.
Dialogue: 10,1:31:55.95,1:32:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment we first connected, \NI realized that you would cry with me.
Dialogue: 10,1:32:03.25,1:32:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that you were my Hibiol.
Dialogue: 10,1:32:09.09,1:32:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When we were together, no matter how sad \Nor painful things got, you lessened my burden.
Dialogue: 10,1:32:19.39,1:32:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, despite all you did...
Dialogue: 10,1:32:24.81,1:32:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You weren't a liar, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:32:28.52,1:32:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You kept our promise.
Dialogue: 10,1:32:32.86,1:32:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been protecting me this whole time.
Dialogue: 10,1:32:38.03,1:32:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,After we separated, I was all alone \Nand I started to lose sight of myself.
Dialogue: 10,1:32:45.62,1:32:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, every time I thought of you...
Dialogue: 10,1:32:49.79,1:32:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I became myself.
Dialogue: 10,1:32:52.76,1:32:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So long as you call for me, it doesn't have to be "Mom".
Dialogue: 10,1:32:58.80,1:33:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you call me, that name \Nwill surely become my own.
Dialogue: 10,1:33:06.39,1:33:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The one who wove who I am now
Dialogue: 10,1:33:09.90,1:33:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,is you.
Dialogue: 10,1:33:22.16,1:33:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia!
Dialogue: 10,1:33:27.41,1:33:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lang!
Dialogue: 10,1:33:29.17,1:33:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you give Ariel a ride?
Dialogue: 10,1:33:33.13,1:33:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take him to Dita and his child.
Dialogue: 10,1:33:36.38,1:33:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To where Ariel calls home.
Dialogue: 10,1:33:50.44,1:33:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go...
Dialogue: 10,1:33:59.82,1:34:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me...
Dialogue: 10,1:34:01.53,1:34:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 10,1:35:10.10,1:35:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we make our way down, Miss Medmel?
Dialogue: 10,1:35:13.27,1:35:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Father?
Dialogue: 10,1:35:19.07,1:35:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,1:35:23.32,1:35:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we descend, an entirely new life awaits.
Dialogue: 10,1:35:29.16,1:35:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, I...
Dialogue: 10,1:35:48.68,1:35:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,1:35:53.23,1:35:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,1:36:00.36,1:36:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You are...
Dialogue: 10,1:36:02.36,1:36:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My... mother?
Dialogue: 10,1:36:10.45,1:36:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Leilia of the Iorph.
Dialogue: 10,1:36:14.04,1:36:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm strongheaded, a tomboy, a shrew.
Dialogue: 10,1:36:20.80,1:36:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And... I am free.
Dialogue: 10,1:36:27.09,1:36:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Leilia, jump!
Dialogue: 10,1:36:43.61,1:36:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fly!
Dialogue: 10,1:36:49.24,1:36:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 10,1:37:08.84,1:37:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maquia...
Dialogue: 10,1:37:12.22,1:37:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,1:37:14.43,1:37:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can fly too.
Dialogue: 10,1:37:22.65,1:37:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 10,1:37:24.32,1:37:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget all about me!
Dialogue: 10,1:37:26.40,1:37:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll forget too!
Dialogue: 10,1:37:28.74,1:37:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't write my days in the castle or this morning into my Hibiol!
Dialogue: 10,1:37:33.87,1:37:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 10,1:37:35.58,1:37:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll let it be forgotten in my long, long memory!
Dialogue: 10,1:37:40.13,1:37:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it all behind!
Dialogue: 10,1:37:42.92,1:37:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... It will just be a tiny tear in the cloth!
Dialogue: 10,1:37:51.55,1:37:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 10,1:37:52.64,1:37:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 10,1:37:53.64,1:37:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother is a very beautiful person.
Dialogue: 10,1:38:01.86,1:38:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Miss Medmel!
Dialogue: 10,1:38:06.07,1:38:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A Renato!
Dialogue: 10,1:38:12.95,1:38:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Leilia...
Dialogue: 10,1:38:16.37,1:38:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We do not need the Renato. We do not need the Iorph.
Dialogue: 10,1:38:20.54,1:38:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The ancient beings are destined to go extinct.
Dialogue: 10,1:38:24.09,1:38:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, we should \Nallow them to live as they please.
Dialogue: 10,1:38:34.35,1:38:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't cry, Leilia.
Dialogue: 10,1:38:41.35,1:38:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay. You'll never forget.
Dialogue: 10,1:38:56.58,1:38:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It hurt so much...
Dialogue: 10,1:38:58.25,1:38:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,1:38:59.87,1:39:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It hurt and tormented me...
Dialogue: 10,1:39:04.42,1:39:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}But I'll never be able to forget such a beautiful world!
Dialogue: 10,1:39:42.79,1:39:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,1:39:46.04,1:39:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You came back...
Dialogue: 10,1:39:49.38,1:39:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,1:39:54.13,1:39:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my...
Dialogue: 10,1:39:56.05,1:39:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,1:40:05.40,1:40:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so soft it's scary.
Dialogue: 10,1:40:13.61,1:40:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to decide on a name.
Dialogue: 10,1:40:16.24,1:40:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,1:40:18.20,1:40:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Dita?
Dialogue: 10,1:40:19.79,1:40:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,1:40:22.66,1:40:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Back when we were kids...
Dialogue: 10,1:40:25.50,1:40:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I said it was weird... to love your mom.
Dialogue: 10,1:40:33.88,1:40:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's not!
Dialogue: 10,1:40:36.34,1:40:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom was so beautiful, so kind...
Dialogue: 10,1:40:44.06,1:40:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,1:40:48.98,1:40:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night, she...
Dialogue: 10,1:40:51.32,1:40:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 10,1:40:53.53,1:40:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too...
Dialogue: 10,1:40:55.78,1:41:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But I... I've always been jealous of your mom!
Dialogue: 10,1:41:04.20,1:41:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom raised me so that I could love you.
Dialogue: 10,1:41:10.04,1:41:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And our girl will one day connect with someone as well.
Dialogue: 10,1:41:13.67,1:41:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's raise her together.
Dialogue: 10,1:41:16.76,1:41:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You and me, the two of us.
Dialogue: 10,1:41:20.43,1:41:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So that she'll be able to love someone.
Dialogue: 10,1:41:30.02,1:41:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The Clan of Partings.
Dialogue: 10,1:41:33.15,1:41:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We watch over a great many partings, \Nand see off that which continues to change.
Dialogue: 10,1:41:39.32,1:41:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Time keeps on moving forward.
Dialogue: 10,1:41:44.54,1:41:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, inevitably, we will connect anew.
Dialogue: 10,1:41:49.96,1:41:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We connect and weave.
Dialogue: 10,1:42:08.56,1:42:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 10,1:42:13.48,1:42:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take me to your grandpa's place?
Dialogue: 10,1:42:17.40,1:42:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Gwandpa?
Dialogue: 10,1:42:18.74,1:42:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lily!
Dialogue: 10,1:42:20.41,1:42:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't run off on your own.
Dialogue: 10,1:42:25.16,1:42:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be...
Dialogue: 10,1:42:30.04,1:42:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother passed away three years ago.
Dialogue: 10,1:42:33.13,1:42:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They were a wonderful couple.
Dialogue: 10,1:42:35.71,1:42:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,After the fall of Mezarte, \NUncle Lang helped them move in here.
Dialogue: 10,1:42:41.72,1:42:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We had our share of hardships, but I believe they lived happy and fulfilling lives.
Dialogue: 10,1:42:52.52,1:42:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 10,1:42:54.06,1:42:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard much about you from them.
Dialogue: 10,1:42:57.32,1:43:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They always spoke of you with a smile.
Dialogue: 10,1:43:00.70,1:43:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you made it in time.
Dialogue: 10,1:43:03.24,1:43:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,My father will soon...
Dialogue: 10,1:43:35.56,1:43:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back,
Dialogue: 10,1:43:36.90,1:43:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:43:48.62,1:43:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You did great, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:43:55.33,1:43:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 10,1:44:00.21,1:44:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You worked hard to live a long, good life, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:44:11.10,1:44:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't cry.
Dialogue: 10,1:44:13.06,1:44:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our... promise.
Dialogue: 10,1:44:30.49,1:44:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome... home.
Dialogue: 10,1:44:42.38,1:44:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 10,1:45:32.14,1:45:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care, Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:45:36.27,1:45:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to be back for dinner.
Dialogue: 10,1:45:46.24,1:45:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For you!
Dialogue: 10,1:45:48.07,1:45:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,1:46:09.97,1:46:12.64,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Mommy! Mommy!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:12.64,1:46:13.93,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:13.93,1:46:15.81,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Listen, listen!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:15.81,1:46:17.56,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:17.56,1:46:18.64,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Morning!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:19.85,1:46:20.85,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I fooled you!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:20.85,1:46:22.77,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,You thought I shed my skin!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:22.77,1:46:24.36,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,What about where I was born?
Dialogue: 10,1:46:24.36,1:46:26.53,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,The tickle bugs are here!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:26.53,1:46:28.24,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,You laughed!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:28.86,1:46:31.28,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,They said that you're different from them.
Dialogue: 10,1:46:31.28,1:46:33.28,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at it...
Dialogue: 10,1:46:33.28,1:46:34.49,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,1:46:35.29,1:46:37.83,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,You don't act like mom when you're here!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:37.83,1:46:40.46,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Don't make her cry!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:40.46,1:46:42.58,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,All I need is you!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:42.58,1:46:43.96,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll protect you.
Dialogue: 10,1:46:43.96,1:46:44.96,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 10,1:46:44.96,1:46:45.59,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Mom?
Dialogue: 10,1:46:45.59,1:46:46.25,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 10,1:46:46.25,1:46:47.09,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,1:46:48.76,1:46:50.43,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 10,1:46:50.76,1:46:51.68,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Over here...
Dialogue: 10,1:46:51.68,1:46:53.64,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 10,1:46:54.76,1:46:56.06,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I hate it.
Dialogue: 10,1:46:56.06,1:46:58.77,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I don't think of you as my mother.
Dialogue: 10,1:46:58.77,1:47:00.52,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I don't understand!
Dialogue: 10,1:47:00.52,1:47:01.98,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I wanted to protect her.
Dialogue: 10,1:47:02.56,1:47:05.19,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Because I can't protect her!
Dialogue: 10,1:47:07.78,1:47:10.11,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Why does she care about me so much?
Dialogue: 10,1:47:10.11,1:47:12.24,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,You taught me so much.
Dialogue: 10,1:47:12.24,1:47:15.49,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Don't leave me, Mom!
Dialogue: 10,1:47:15.49,1:47:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ariel, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,1:47:18.50,1:47:19.75,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Mommy?
Dialogue: 10,1:47:20.46,1:47:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 10,1:47:22.37,1:47:24.17,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I won't cry!
Dialogue: 10,1:47:24.17,1:47:26.63,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm your mom, after all!
Dialogue: 10,1:47:27.30,1:47:28.88,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 10,1:47:29.67,1:47:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom... is going to break our promise...
Dialogue: 10,1:47:39.89,1:47:41.39,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Mommy!
Dialogue: 10,1:47:45.94,1:47:48.15,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Mommy, I love you!
Dialogue: 10,1:47:49.90,1:47:51.57,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I love you!
Dialogue: 10,1:48:04.08,1:48:05.25,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Ariel...
Dialogue: 10,1:48:11.59,1:48:12.84,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Ariel...
Dialogue: 10,1:48:32.86,1:48:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All finished?
Dialogue: 10,1:48:35.11,1:48:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the end.
Dialogue: 10,1:48:36.87,1:48:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as I'm alive, Ariel's Hibiol will continue on.
Dialogue: 10,1:48:45.33,1:48:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't laugh at me!
Dialogue: 10,1:48:47.21,1:48:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The Elder would laugh too if she saw your face.
Dialogue: 10,1:48:57.68,1:49:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She'd laugh from the joy of learning from you that not all partings have to be sad.
Dialogue: 10,1:49:08.19,1:49:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop on, we're going.
Dialogue: 10,1:49:10.11,1:49:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,On a journey to connect with \Nthe next person you'll part with.
Dialogue: 10,1:49:21.79,1:49:23.08,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,Elder.
Dialogue: 10,1:49:24.37,1:49:31.38,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was able to love Ariel.
Dialogue: 10,1:49:33.34,1:49:37.22,Default Italic,,0,0,0,,I'm glad that I loved.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.27,1:49:53.94,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}chippoke na hoshi yo
Dialogue: 0,1:49:47.27,1:49:53.94,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}on a planet oh so small
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.73,1:50:05.91,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}mawari tsudzukete afuresou ni
Dialogue: 0,1:49:54.73,1:50:05.91,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}continuing to turn, cradling gently
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.91,1:50:20.80,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}kagayaite nagareteyuku \Nkirei na mama de
Dialogue: 0,1:50:05.91,1:50:20.80,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}twinkling drops of life, \Neach one shining beautifully
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.16,1:50:59.13,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}arukidasu ai wo tsurete \Nkanaderu you ni
Dialogue: 0,1:50:44.16,1:50:59.13,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}let us step forward, love in our hands, \Nhumming a melody
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.13,1:51:09.98,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}shinjiteru donna katachi demo
Dialogue: 0,1:50:59.13,1:51:09.98,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}believing that no matter how it may appear
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.98,1:51:21.57,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}taiyou wa noboru kara kitto
Dialogue: 0,1:51:09.98,1:51:21.57,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}the sun will surely rise once more
