Dialogue: 0,1:51:34.83,1:51:42.34,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}on this planet oh so small
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.34,1:51:53.48,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}ochita namida wa afuresou na
Dialogue: 0,1:51:42.34,1:51:53.48,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}each tear that falls will fill up our hearts
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.48,1:52:00.57,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}yasashisa wo misetekureru
Dialogue: 0,1:51:53.48,1:52:00.57,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}until they overflow with kindness
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.57,1:52:09.91,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,500)}mou ichido waratte
Dialogue: 0,1:52:00.57,1:52:09.91,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,500)}so please laugh again
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.61,1:52:58.58,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,800)}sono mune no naka ni wa nani ga aru no?
Dialogue: 0,1:52:42.61,1:52:58.58,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,800)}please tell me what it is you hide in your heart
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.59,1:53:16.64,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}arukidasu ai ni natte hikari no naka e
Dialogue: 0,1:53:01.59,1:53:16.64,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}let us step forward, becoming love, into the light
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.64,1:53:27.41,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}daijoubu donna mirai demo
Dialogue: 0,1:53:16.64,1:53:27.41,viator,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\fad(250,250)}we will make it through \Nno matter what the future holds
Dialogue: 0,1:53:27.41,1:53:39.46,viator,,0,0,0,,{\an7\blur0.5\fad(250,500)}taiyou wa noboru kara kitto
